--- SW-BA1-Geral --- 
enable
configure terminal
hostname SW-BA1-Geral
no ip domain-lookup


--- Paste do vlan_config.txt --- 

--- link's e portas em trunk mode ---
 conf t
 interface range e0/0-3 , e3/0
 switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
 switchport mode trunk
 switchport trunk native vlan 60
 switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,20,50,60,70,80,90,999
 no shutdown


--- link's e portas em access mode ---
conf t 
interface e1/0
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 70
// depois de ter routing estavel
//switchport port-security maximum 1
//switchport port-security mac-address sticky 
//switchport port-security violation restrict
spanning-tree portfast

interface e1/1
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 80
// depois de ter routing estavel
//switchport port-security maximum 1
//switchport port-security mac-address sticky 
//switchport port-security violation restrict
spanning-tree portfast
end

